                    <p class="figure-caption-description">“<em>Kriya Yoga</em>, the scientific technique of God-realization,” Babaji said to Yogananda, “will ultimately spread in all lands, and aid in harmonizing the nations through man’s personal, transcendental perception of the Infinite Father.”</p>
