                    </a>
                            <span></span>
                </h3>
                    <p class="figure-caption-description">The three wise men that visited Jesus Christ after his birth, Paramhansa Yogananda said, were Lahiri Mahasaya, Swami Sri Yukteswar, and Mahavatar Babaji.

In his travels to India, Jesus is said to have paid them a return visit.</p>
